{"title":"Incentives matter","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/874893008/0/marginalrevolution~Incentives-matter.html","date":1712078985000,"content":"<blockquote>\r\n<p>Why are so many random government agents claiming to be suffering from Havana Syndrome?</p>\r\n<p>The devil is in the details…</p>\r\n<p>The HAVANA Act, which passed in 2021, gives an untaxed lump-sum payment of one years' salary to government employees with a \"neurological injury.\"</p>\r\n<p>— Jordan Schachtel @ dossier.today (@JordanSchachtel) <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://twitter.com/JordanSchachtel/status/1774810712684081190?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 1, 2024</a></p></blockquote>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>(To be clear, I do take the Havana Syndrome allegations seriously, but the broader equilibrium is worth pondering too.)</p>\r\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/04/incentives-matter-3.html\">Incentives matter</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com\">Marginal REVOLUTION</a>.</p>\r\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" src=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/874893008/0/marginalrevolution\" />\r\n<div><a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/874893008/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/874893008/marginalrevolution,\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/874893008/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/x.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/19/874893008/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/email20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/20/874893008/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=